      "cooked": "<p>pjer, pa provo te shkruash poezi, do te kesh me shum sukses se ne proze.</p>\n<p>Bej nje vjershe me titull <em>“Poezi politike pa një pa dy”</em> qe fillon:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>O Pallosh, o Malok,</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>nuk shihni ç’ben Kone Miushi?</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>hedh gurin, fsheh doren,</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>e nxjerr kemben (e trete)</em> etj etj</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>ose:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>O parti te medha,</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>hapni rruge partive t’vogla,</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>sepse i vogli e ka t’modh</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>(koefiçentin makroekonomik)</em> etj etj</p>\n</blockquote>",
